---
import Layout from '../layouts/layouts.astro';
---
<Layout title="About">
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 text-gray-300">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-12 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500 mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">About Hossain Exim International</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Established in the early 2000s, Hossain Exim International has grown to become one of Bangladesh's most trusted importers and distributors of premium steel products. We are dedicated to delivering excellence and reliability in every partnership.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        We specialize in sourcing high-quality steel from reputable manufacturers worldwide, supplying a diverse range of products to construction companies, fabricators, and industrial clients across Bangladesh.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start">
                            <div class="bg-blue-600 p-3 rounded-full mr-4 shadow-lg">
                                <span class="fas fa-check text-white text-lg"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-white mb-1">Quality Assurance</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-400">Rigorous quality control and inspection at every stage of procurement and distribution to guarantee product integrity.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-start">
                            <div class="bg-purple-600 p-3 rounded-full mr-4 shadow-lg">
                                <span class="fas fa-truck text-white text-lg"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-white mb-1">Nationwide Distribution Network</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-400">A robust logistics network ensures timely and efficient delivery to clients in every corner of Bangladesh.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-start">
                            <div class="bg-pink-600 p-3 rounded-full mr-4 shadow-lg">
                                <span class="fas fa-handshake text-white text-lg"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-white mb-1">Customer-Centric Approach</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-400">Our dedicated support team works closely with clients to provide tailored solutions that meet their specific needs.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="md:w-1/2 relative flex justify-center items-center">
    <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-600 bg-gray-800 text-center animate-fade-in">
        <div class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-purple-500 mb-2">2000</div>
        <div class="text-gray-400 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">Year Established</div>
    </div>
</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500"></div>

    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 text-gray-300">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-red-500 text-center mb-12 animate-fade-in-up">Our Leadership & Team</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
                <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-700 text-center transform transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">
                    <div class="w-28 h-28 mx-auto rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-4 border-4 border-cyan-500">
                        <img src="/images/imamhossain.jpg" alt="CEO Name" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Imam Hossain</h3>
                    <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold mb-2">Chief Executive Officer</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">A visionary leader with over two decades of experience in the steel import industry, driving our commitment to excellence.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-700 text-center transform transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">
                    <div class="w-28 h-28 mx-auto rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-4 border-4 border-purple-500">
                        <img src="/images/robiulpitu.jpg" alt="Manager Name" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Robiul Kader Pitu</h3>
                    <p class="text-purple-400 font-semibold mb-2">General Manager</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Overseeing daily operations and ensuring seamless coordination across all departments to maintain our high standards.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-700 text-center transform transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">
                    <div class="w-28 h-28 mx-auto rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-4 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-700 border-4 border-pink-500">
                        <span class="text-5xl text-gray-500 fas fa-users"></span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Our Team</h3>
                    <p class="text-pink-400 font-semibold mb-2">Dedicated Professionals</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">A dedicated team of over 20 employees working tirelessly to meet our clients' needs and exceed expectations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>